g 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/slipknot-clown@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">Slipknot</a>的 Shawn &#39;Clown&#39; Crahan 谈到了乐队“丢失的专辑”“Look Outside Your Window”的推迟。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353">活结乐队的小丑谈论 2024 年巡演和新材料：“这支乐队从未如此快乐”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该歌曲由主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">Corey Taylor</a> 、Sid Wilson、Jim Root 和 Shawn &#39;Clown&#39; Crahan 录制，当时乐队正在制作 2008 年的歌曲“All Hope Is Gone”。有一次，泰勒试图将两张唱片合二为一，但“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-slipknot-all-hope-is-hope-gone-outtakes-experimental-radiohead-2541951">超级实验性的、充满活力的</a>”曲目并没有融合在一起。迄今为止，仅发布了一首曲目——“All Hope Is Gone”的附赠曲目“Til We Die”。</p><p>这张专辑长期以来一直受到参与成员的调侃，主唱科里·泰勒(Corey Taylor)去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-teases-release-of-slipknots-lost-album-look-outside-your-window-3482056">调侃这张专辑的发行</a>，再次火上浇油。此后专辑的进展有所加快，《小丑》现在提供了这张期待已久的唱片的最新消息。 </p><figure id="attachment_3600001" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3600001" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3600001" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/slipknot-corey-taylor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3600001" class="wp-caption-text">活结乐团的科里·泰勒。图片来源：Venla Shalin/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>这位打击乐手兼乐队领军人物在接受<a href="https://www.vulture.com/article/slipknot-clown-shawn-crahan-best-songs.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Vulture</em></a>采访时谈到 Slipknot 未发行的作品时说道：“我什至不知道从哪里开始。我的意思是，有音频，然后还有视频。我们有大量不完整的概念，有些刚刚完成。我希望文化中能够有很多活结。在我的整个职业生涯中，我创造了很多东西，但真正付诸实践的却非常非常少。”</p><p>然后他谈到了《看看窗外》，并补充道：“没有人相信它存在，或者它会出现。我一直高度评价它，我总是说你永远不会听到科里·泰勒这样唱歌。在我看来，这只是一种完全不同的方法。最近，我批准了所有的艺术作品。我也非常努力地混合和掌握它。”</p><p>该乐队今年还忙着举行 25 周年巡演，并宣布了 2025 年在多个地区进行巡演。他们最近分享了 2025 年欧洲巡演的日期，该巡演定于明年夏天开始。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-2025-european-tour-3809436">您可以在此处找到完整的日期列表和票务信息</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3774132" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3774132" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3774132" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min.jpg" alt="活结乐队的 Shawn “Clown” Crahan 摄影：Chelsea Guglielmino" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Shawn-Clown-Crahan-of-Slipknot-photo-by-Chelsea-Guglielmino-min-1068x678.jpg 1068w" 