/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/celine-dion">席琳·迪翁 (Celine Dion)</a>向她已故的“珍贵导师”<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/quincy-jones">昆西·琼斯 (Quincy Jones)</a>致敬 - 看看她在下面怎么说。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="650" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/quincy-jones-obituary-3809386"><b>昆西·琼斯，1933-2024：眼中闪烁着光芒打破界限的超级制片人</b></a></li></ul><p>周一（11 月 4 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-producer-and-songwriter-quincy-jones-has-died-aged-91-3809203">传奇制作人昆西·琼斯去世的消息传出，享年 91 岁</a>。随着他的去世，人们纷纷向这位已故偶像表示敬意。现在，席琳·迪翁也加入了这一行列，并在社交媒体上为琼斯写了一篇纪念文章。 </p><figure id="attachment_3809934" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809934" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809934" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/celine-dion-quincy-jones-2010@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809934" class="wp-caption-text"> 2010 年，席琳·迪翁和昆西·琼斯一起在录音室。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>在 Instagram 上发布的一篇帖子中，附有两张她与已故制作人的照片以及两张她与琼斯合作的图片，她写道：“得知我的朋友、唯一的音乐天才昆西·琼斯去世的消息，我感到心碎。昆西既是一位我所珍视的导师，也是我尊敬的人，因为他对几乎所有形式的美国音乐都产生了深远的影响，这触动了我的世界。”</p><p> “我很荣幸能与昆西一起工作，这是梦想成真，”迪翁继续说道。 “在我们的会议中，他的音乐直觉非常深刻——他帮助我捕捉到了‘天堂的一小部分’。昆西总是确切地知道每首歌需要什么。</p><p> “除了他的善良和无数的成就之外，我还钦佩他的慈善工作，造福于艺术、全球饥荒和贫困青年。他的影响力确实延伸到了全球各个角落！”</p><p>请参阅下面席琳·迪翁的完整帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCAKQFzxRVC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xm