运动，但我认为它们都是同一个公司硬币的两面。</p><p> “从情感上来说，一个有色人种女性等等——当然，让我们把它排除在外，勾选那个框，这样我们就可以继续前进。但是，就人们真正想要的东西而言，两党都没有提供——他们只是控制了权力，”他继续说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3488914" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3488914" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3488914" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-strokes-all-points-east-1@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3488914" class="wp-caption-text"> The Strokes 乐队的 Julian Casablancas 在 2023 年 All Points East Festival 上表演。图片来源：Jim Dyson/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩(Chappell Roan)</a>今年早些时候也发表过类似言论，当时她表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-on-why-she-feels-no-pressure-to-officially-endorse-a-presidential-candidate-3796272">，由于双方都存在“问题”，她不会在选举中全力支持任何一位候选人</a>。然而，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-clears-up-elections-stance-im-voting-for-fucking-kamala-3797165">后来表示她将投票给哈里斯</a>，尽管这并不一定意味着她支持副总统。</p><p>许多知名演员、艺术家和音乐家在选举前公开支持两位候选人。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-endorses-kamala-harris-at-houston-rally-im-here-as-a-mother-3806513">上个月</a>在民主党关于生殖权利的集会上发表讲话，比莉·艾利什<a href="http://xn--her%20song%20when%20the%20partys%20over%20for%20a%20democrats%20ad%20on%20reproductive%20care-pw43didiv/">批准了她的歌曲</a>《When the Party&#39;s Over》为民主党生殖保健广告， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/avengers-cast-reunite-to-endorse-kamala-harris-kamala-forever-3808508">漫威《<i>复仇者联盟》</i>的演员们</a>在 Instagram 视频中重聚，为哈里斯背书。</p><p>其他正式认可哈里斯的人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-shares-endorsement-for-kamala-harris-3808708">麦当娜</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/st-vincent-endorses-kamala-harris-says-her-grandmother-wouldnt-have-stood-for-disrespect-from-trump-3808930">圣文森特</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jennifer-lopez-on-puerto-rican-heritage-after-trump-rally-joke-we-are-americans-3809017">詹妮弗·洛佩兹</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-john-legend-and-more-endorse-kamala-harris-for-us-president-3776745">查理·XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchell-shares-her-thoughts-on-the-us-elections-fuck-donald-trump-3804542">乔尼·米切尔</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-on-eve-of-us-election-3809580">Lady Gaga</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cher-endorses-kamala-harris-im-so-grateful-to-be-able-to-make-my-voice-count-this-year-3804267">雪儿</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-speaks-at-kamala-harris-rally-hits-out-at-donald-trumps-comments-about-detroit-3804404">利佐</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/obama-raps-lose-yourself-verse-at-kamala-harris-rally-after-being-introduced-by-eminem-3805325">阿姆</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/usher-joins-kamala-harris-at-atlanta-rally-everything-we-do-in-the-next-17-days-will-affect-our-children-and-grandchildren-3804493">亚瑟小子</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-perform-what-about-us-with-daughter-to-close-de